title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: 2X GTA$ and RP on Cayo Perico Motor Wars
content:
Pull the ripcord and fight to survive in Cayo Perico Motor Wars to win glory and Double Rewards for a second week running. Join the Cayo Perico Series to get involved.

GTA+ Members parachuting onto the island paradise will also continue to earn a whopping 4X GTA$ and RP.
